name: Crunchy Network
public_notice: Crunchy DAO (CRDAO) & Crunchy Network (CRUNCH) have merged into a new token, Crunchy Network (CRNCHY) with a new contract. For more information, please view these announcements on Twitter and Medium.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: CRUNCH is the utility token of crunchy.network. It will aid funding development and will be able to be used to pay for service fees and/or to pay reduced service fees. Additionally some services may require that you hold a certain amount of CRUNCH in your wallet in order to utilize the service.
